full_text: My test results posted & I have a bad feeling. Low Red Blood Cell Count, low creatine, low potassium, low calcium... low platelet count but the platelets are larger than normal.  I have a feeling I'm losing blood somewhere & it is making me feel like crap.
Hey @pulte I was watching some Chris Hansen interviews on Youtube today and he said he grew up and went to school in Detroit with your family.  Thought that was kind of interesting for him to say,
